A vast crystalline network of interconnected nodes floating in deep space, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures and warm lighting. The nodes appear as glowing orbs of different sizes—some tiny like fireflies, others large like luminous moons—all connected by delicate golden threads that pulse with gentle energy. In the foreground, a small figure sits on one of the larger orbs, thoughtfully observing the sprawling web around them. Some clusters of nodes are tightly organized in neat geometric patterns while others drift chaotically in loose tangles. The color palette shifts from cool indigos and teals in the distant background to warm ambers and soft corals near the central figure, suggesting the tension between structure and simplicity. Wispy clouds drift between the connections, and tiny spirit-like creatures swim through the network like curious fish exploring coral reefs.
